      "parameters": {
        "prompt": "=Map this LangGraph API response into the compliance triage JSON schema below.\n- overall_risk: use LangGraph overall_risk\n- findings: map each LangGraph finding (contract_clause_id, matched_regulatory_source, matched_regulatory_article, verdict, risk, justification, confidence)\n- routing_decision: High → escalation, Medium → reviewer_queue, Low → auto_file\n- jurisdiction, parties, contract_type: from Node 4b extracted fields (pass them in the same prompt if needed)\n- rag_insight: use report_markdown\n- confidence: average of finding confidences, or max finding confidence\nDo not return unknown placeholders if LangGraph findings are present.\nReport to clean:\n{{ JSON.stringify($('Run LangGraph Audit').item.json) }}"
